topPRs.body:
This PR adds a refactored autocoder plugin as well as the new github and e2b plugins.

Instead of merging this in, we should verify we're happy with this and then probably push it out to its own repo (along with plugin deps).

However, for arch design reasons, nice to do it in the monorepo and work here while we polish it.

topPRs.title: Add planning plugin
topPRs.author: lalalune
topPRs.body:
This PR builds on: https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/pull/5505

The goal of this plugin is to add an additional planning action which does a more detailed and high-compute version of the initial decision handler in the agent's message handling plugin (i.e. the default handler).

This plans a set of sub-actions which will run in order.

Our goal is to use this plugin as a testbed for action planning and benchmarking, especially against the REALM benchmark, which is included.
